Terminals which are not used

   ERROR
   ILLEGAL_TOK


Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: declList

    2 declList: decl
    3         | declList decl

    4 decl: varDecl
    5     | funDecl

    6 varDecl: typeSpecifier ID SEMICLN
    7        | typeSpecifier ID arrayDecl SEMICLN

    8 funcTypeName: typeSpecifier ID

    9 typeSpecifier: KWD_INT
   10              | KWD_CHAR
   11              | KWD_VOID

   12 funDecl: funcTypeName LPAREN RPAREN funBody
   13        | funcTypeName LPAREN formalDeclList RPAREN funBody

   14 formalDeclList: formalDecl
   15               | formalDeclList COMMA formalDecl

   16 formalDecl: typeSpecifier ID
   17           | typeSpecifier ID LSQ_BRKT RSQ_BRKT

   18 arrayDecl: LSQ_BRKT INTCONST RSQ_BRKT

   19 funBody: LCRLY_BRKT localDeclList statementList RCRLY_BRKT

   20 localDeclList: /* empty */
   21              | varDecl localDeclList

   22 statementList: /* empty */
   23              | statement statementList

   24 statement: compoundStmt
   25          | assignStmt
   26          | condStmt
   27          | loopStmt
   28          | returnStmt
   29          | expression SEMICLN

   30 compoundStmt: LCRLY_BRKT statementList RCRLY_BRKT

   31 assignStmt: var OPER_ASGN expression SEMICLN

   32 forAssign: var OPER_ASGN expression

   33 condStmt: KWD_IF LPAREN expression RPAREN statement
   34         | KWD_IF LPAREN expression RPAREN statement KWD_ELSE statement

   35 loopStmt: KWD_WHILE LPAREN expression RPAREN statement
   36         | KWD_FOR LPAREN forAssign SEMICLN expression SEMICLN forAssign RPAREN statement

   37 returnStmt: KWD_RETURN SEMICLN
   38           | KWD_RETURN expression SEMICLN

   39 var: ID
   40    | ID LSQ_BRKT addExpr RSQ_BRKT

   41 expression: addExpr
   42           | expression relop addExpr

   43 relop: OPER_LTE
   44      | OPER_LT
   45      | OPER_GT
   46      | OPER_GTE
   47      | OPER_EQ
   48      | OPER_NEQ

   49 addExpr: term
   50        | addExpr addop term

   51 addop: OPER_ADD
   52      | OPER_SUB

   53 term: factor
   54     | term mulop factor

   55 mulop: OPER_MUL
   56      | OPER_DIV

   57 factor: LPAREN expression RPAREN
   58       | var
   59       | funCallExpr
   60       | INTCONST
   61       | CHARCONST

   62 @1: /* empty */

   63 funCallExpr: ID LPAREN @1 argList RPAREN

   64 @2: /* empty */

   65 funCallExpr: ID LPAREN @2 RPAREN

   66 argList: expression
   67        | argList COMMA expression


